OL,6,FAn ice cream vendor suffered
OL,7,F"catastrophic injuries" when he was
OL,8,Fattacked from behind and repeatedly
OL,9,Fstabbed on the ground, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FShazad Khan, 41, was allegedly set
OL,13,Fupon by Zaher Zaarour while he was
OL,14,Fplying his trade in Monks Park in
OL,15,FWembley, north-west London, on the
OL,16,Fevening of Tuesday 19 August.
OL,18,FAt about 6pm, Mr Khan was in his van
OL,19,Fwhen he was approached by the
OL,20,Fdefendant who engaged him in a
OL,21,Fdiscussion, it is claimed.
