OL,3,CIce cream vendor suffered
OL,4,C'catastrophic' injuries, court told
OL,6,F"He reached round the front of Mr Khan
OL,7,Fand stabbed him to the right side of
OL,8,Fhis chest. That blow alone caused
OL,9,Fcatastrophic injuries to Mr Khan. That
OL,10,Fwas caught on CCTV."
OL,12,FWitnesses then allegedly saw the
OL,13,Fdefendant cut Mr Khan's throat and
OL,14,Frepeatedly stab the left side of his
OL,15,Fbody with "severe force", the Old
OL,16,FBailey heard.
OL,18,FMr Hallam said the stab wounds were
OL,19,F"consistent with a focused and intense
OL,20,Fattack while Mr Khan was on the ground
OL,21,Fand the defendant was over him".
