OL,6,FDetails of the incident were heard as
OL,7,Fhe made his first appearance at the
OL,8,FOld Bailey for a preliminary hearing
OL,9,Fbefore Judge Nigel Lickley KC.
OL,11,FBearded Zaarour appeared in the dock
OL,12,Fwearing a grey T-shirt and spoke only
OL,13,Fto confirm his identity.
OL,15,FJudge Lickley set a plea hearing for
OL,16,FNovember 12 and a provisional three-
OL,17,Fweek trial from April 7 next year.
