OL,6,FRemanding into custody, the judge
OL,7,Foutlined the allegation, saying: "The
OL,8,Fincident, some which is captured on
OL,9,FCCTV, includes it is said the first
OL,10,Fstabbing action by the defendant to
OL,11,Fthe victim while the victim had his
OL,12,Fback turned to him.
OL,14,F"He straddled the deceased and
OL,15,Fcontinued to stab him multiple times,
OL,16,Fcausing him catastrophic injuries so
OL,17,Fas by the time emergency services
OL,18,Farrived, Mr Khan had died at the
OL,19,Fscene."
